###############################################################################
# OBJECTIVE
###############################################################################
Implement proper cleanup of async operations when leaving screens to optimize memory
and prevent unnecessary requests.

###############################################################################
# REQUIREMENTS
###############################################################################
requirements:
  - Create cleanup utility for async operations (AbortController)
  - Implement cleanup hooks for screen unmount/navigation
  - Cancel pending API requests when leaving screen
  - Clear timeouts and intervals on cleanup
  - Remove event listeners to prevent memory leaks
  - Log cleanup operations for debugging
  - Apply to all major screens (Objects, History, Tracking, Reports)

###############################################################################
# DELIVERABLES
###############################################################################
out: [Async operation cleanup system]
done:
  - No API requests continue after screen exit
  - Memory usage optimized with proper cleanup
  - AbortController pattern implemented consistently
  - Cleanup hooks integrated with React lifecycle
ref: @navitrack-apps/src-client/CODE_MAP.md (API layer, screen components).
